= AGUA

The Next generation UI Framework for aqua

== DEMO

 $ npm install
 $ NODE_ENV=production node bin/www
 $ chormium http://localhost:3000

== RULES

// * Never commit any component without test or die
 * Be super super portable, swappable and customizable or die

== 2 Kinds :

 * Container ... as a container of Devices and controlling it
 * Device ... provides specific feature to view information or to input something for a user


          ---------------Container-----------------
          |                                    |
          |              Device                |
          |                                    |
          |--------------Container----------------|
          |           |                        |
          |           |                        |
          |    D      L                        |
          |    e      a                        |
          |    v      y         Device         |
          |    i      o                        |
          |    c      u                        |
          |    e      t                        |
          |           |                        |
          --------------------------------------

